JavaPythonNode.jsGo <p>Replace the <code>@LocalStackContainer</code> module with the Floci module:</p> pom.xml<pre><code>&lt;!-- Before --&gt;
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;org.testcontainers&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;localstack&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;

&lt;!-- After --&gt;
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;io.github.hectorvent&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;floci-testcontainers&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;LATEST&lt;/version&gt;
  &lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
</code></pre> <p>See the Java Testcontainers guide for full setup.</p> <p>See the Python Testcontainers guide.</p> <p>See the Node.js Testcontainers guide.</p> <p>See the Go Testcontainers guide.</p>

MavenGradle <pre><code>&lt;dependency&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;io.floci&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;testcontainers-floci&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;1.4.0&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
</code></pre> <pre><code>testImplementation 'io.floci:testcontainers-floci:1.4.0'
</code></pre>
